### -- FAZA 2 SMOKE TEST --

### Lista persoane (verificare seed)
GET {{host}}/api/Persoane
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

### Detalii persoană (presupun id=1 = Andrei Mihalache, primar Slobozia)
GET {{host}}/api/Persoane/1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

### Lista MandateFunctie
GET {{host}}/api/MandateFunctie
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

### Lista MandateFunctie — filtru pe Primar
GET {{host}}/api/MandateFunctie?tipFunctie=1
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

### Creare Persoană nouă
POST {{host}}/api/Persoane
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "numeComplet": "Persoană Test Nouă",
  "email": "test.nou@example.com",
  "telefon": "0720123456"
}

### Tentativă creare al 2-lea Primar pe Slobozia — așteptăm 409 (suprapunere)
POST {{host}}/api/MandateFunctie
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipFunctie": 1,
  "persoanaId": 2,
  "dataInceput": "2024-10-27",
  "nrActNumire": "HCL test conflict"
}

### Tentativă viceprimar pe consilier fără mandat (Test Filtru = consilier 3 are mandat, deci ar trebui să meargă)
POST {{host}}/api/MandateFunctie
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipFunctie": 2,
  "consilierId": 2,
  "dataInceput": "2024-10-27",
  "nrActNumire": "HCL Vasile vp"
}

### Închidere mandat (presupun id=3 = viceprimarul Ion seedat)
POST {{host}}/api/MandateFunctie/3/Inchide
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataSfarsit": "2025-06-15"
}

### Detalii comisie cu includeIstoric (nu e crucial — verifică doar parser query param)
GET {{host}}/api/Comisii/1?includeIstoric=true
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}


