### Setare SMTP Slobozia (Mailtrap sandbox)
PUT https://localhost:7006/api/Smtp
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "host": "sandbox.smtp.mailtrap.io",
  "port": 2525,
  "utilizator": "b6f4711dbd2bfb",
  "parola": "0c0be1bb71a7a5",
  "emailFrom": "no-reply@slobozia.ro",
  "numeFrom": "Primăria Slobozia",
  "securitate": 1
}


